    "It must therefore be novel, or markedly improve an existing approach.",
    "(iii) Validation research (VR), a paper exploring a DM-ML technique in clinical practice.",
    "(iv) review, a paper assessing the literature of DM-ML as an adjunct to GYN oncology.",
    "(v) Others, e.g.",
    "experience reports, philosophical papers, opinion papers."
